name: Alexis Patel
summary: Alexis Patel, 33, is a non-binary individual who uses they/them pronouns. They hold a graduate degree and work as a Program Director in the non-profit industry. Alexis is multilingual, speaking English, Spanish, and Hindi. They were originally from Houston, Texas but currently reside in Los Angeles, California. Alexis is spiritual and politically liberal. They're a parent and have no intention to have more children. Alexis also owns a dog. In their spare time, Alexis enjoys traveling, reading, painting, and volunteering. Alexis is an active individual and maintains a healthy lifestyle, including moderate drinking but no smoking, marijuana, or drug use. As a Virgo with an MBTI personality type of INFJ, they're seeking a partner aged between 30 and 40 who shares their lifestyle choices and has the same preferences regarding children.
